711172f-a.text:
13th Street, north side, west from 135 West 13th Street between
Sixth and Seventh Avenues.
March 6, 1933.
P. L. Sperr.

711173f-a.text:
(1)
Greenwich Presbyterian Church, 145 West 13th Street, north side, between Sixth and Seventh Avenues. This was established in 1846 as the Thirteenth Street Presbyterian Church; the present name was adopted in 1910.
June, 1929.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2)
A clear view of the same, two years later.
May 28, 1931.

P.L.Sperr
